\begin_layout Standard
A variety of benchmark test functions were employed to comprehensively evaluate the performance of the proposed PEAO algorithm.
 The selected benchmark problems were chosen from the well-established BBOB benchmark suite and have been widely adopted in the continuous black-box optimization literature 
